data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 4 bedroom 2 bath house in the highly sought out Pleasant Hill neighborhood. As soon as you walk in the front door you'll notice the extreme attention to detail, the custom lockers in the foyer that add an inviting touch. The cozy seating area with an electric fire place to keep you warm during the cold months, upgraded celling fans, hardware and so much more! Make your way outside to your own personal oasis, you'll notice a newly built pergola with pavers full equipped with electricity, and a deck to entertain with and enjoy! This home has so much to offer including a 2.5% assumable rate! Schedule a private showing today!
